                        </tr>
                    </tbody>
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <p class="examples-note">
        *This web application, E-payments, and/or Richard Choi, pertaining to the party that created this website application, is not responsible for any potential alleged data loss such as but not limited to card number(s), expiration date(s) and/or security number(s) and/or alleged payments that are made on the actual card.*

    </p>

